我将批量从最新的 .backup.\* 文件恢复受损源文件，然后重新运行类型检查验证修复效果。随后再根据剩余错误做逐步清理。

---

```bash
bash -lc "set -euo pipefail; shopt -s nullglob; declare -A restored; while IFS= read -r -d '' f; do files+=("$f"); done < <(find . -type f -name "*.backup.*" -print0); if ((${#files[@]}==0)); then echo 'No backup files found'; exit 0; fi; IFS=$'\n' sorted=($(ls -t -- "${files[@]}")); for f in "${sorted[@]}"; do base=${f%%.backup.*}; if [[ -z ${restored[$base]+x} ]]; then mkdir -p "$(dirname "$base")"; cp -f -- "$f" "$base"; restored[$base]=1; echo "Restored $base <- $f"; fi; done; echo "Restored ${#restored[@]} files.""
```
